# 💰 Contract Cost Optimization & Spend Analysis

## 🧠 Problem Statement
Organizations often face cost inefficiencies due to lack of structured spend visibility across vendor contracts.  
This project focuses on identifying cost-saving opportunities through **data-driven contract analysis**.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Excel (Advanced, Pivot Tables, VBA)
- Data Analysis Techniques
- Financial Modeling

---

## 🔍 Key Steps
- Analyzed historical vendor spend data  
- Identified cost leakage and inefficiencies  
- Built automated cost tracking model  
- Performed variance and trend analysis  

---

## 📈 Key Insights
- Detected key areas of unnecessary spend  
- Highlighted patterns in vendor pricing inconsistencies  
- Enabled deeper visibility into contract financials  

---

## 💼 Business Impact
- Contributed to **£2M cost savings** through data-backed insights  
- Improved financial transparency across contracts  
- Supported strategic vendor negotiations  

---

## 📌 Key Features
- Automated spend tracking system  
- Monthly reporting framework  
- Variance analysis dashboard  

